ActInternational Interests in Mobile Equipment (aircraft equipment) Act
Jobs and Growth Act, 2012
SubjectOrder Fixing April 1, 2013 as the Day on which the Provisions of the International Interests in Mobile Equipment (aircraft equipment) Act that are not in force, and Sections 414 to 423 of the Jobs and Growth Act, 2012 Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing April 1, 2013 as the day on which (1) the heading before section 1, sections 1 to 9.1 and Schedules 1 to 3 of the INTERNATIONAL INTERESTS IN MOBILE EQUIPMENT (AIRCRAFT EQUIPMENT) ACT, chapter 3 of the Statutes of Canada, 2005; and (2) sections 414 to 423 of the JOBS AND GROWTH ACT, 2012, chapter 31 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2013-0026 Publication Date: 2013-03-27
